flowchart LR
    ClientA([Client A])
    ClientB([Client B])
    Collab[Collaboration Server<br/>per-doc actor<br/>OT / CRDT merge]
    DocStore[(Document Store<br/>snapshots + op log)]
    Snapshot[Snapshot Service<br/>periodic compaction]

    ClientA <-->|ops + rev| Collab
    ClientB <-->|ops + rev| Collab
    Collab -.->|broadcast| ClientA
    Collab -.->|broadcast| ClientB
    Collab -->|persist ops| DocStore
    Snapshot <--> DocStore

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class ClientA,ClientB external
    class Collab,Snapshot service
